Incoming livestream: setting clear accountability for the experimentation teams and security and IT, and additional review processes and preventive and detective controls.


242
00:41:18.945 --> 00:41:19.865
Incoming livestream: So…


243
00:41:20.105 --> 00:41:34.425
Incoming livestream: I'll… you know, that was our governance structure and how we set about doing, you know, respond… securely enabling AI in the enterprise. I want to talk a little bit more into how we actually


